title: SNES for PS2+roms,ESR&FREEMCBOOT
description:
SNES Emulator that runs on the ps2 platform This is an NTSC disc but like my other ps2 torrents can be converted easily to PAL using the instructions provided. only three things make this copy of SNES STATION stand out from the others I have found 


1. The roms are not zipped. (snes station supports .zip but they have lower compatibility)

2.It Is esr patched (iv'e found many that i could not patch until i modified them a little).

3. There are many rom hacks in this that ive found from various sources including a few excellent fan-made 16 bit remakes of 8-bit classics.
